{"word":"ἐπίκλησις","slug":"ἐπίκλησις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n39754\" key=\"e)pi/klhsis\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἐπί-κλησις</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">εως</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, <sense id=\"n39754.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">surname, additional name</tr_>; used by <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> </bibl> only in acc. abs., <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">like</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">ἐπίκλην</ref></xr>, and mostly <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπίκλησιν καλέειν</foreign>, as <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Ἀστυάναξ</foreign>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὃν Τρῶες ἐπίκλησιν καλέουσιν</foreign> Astyanax, as they call him <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">by surname</tr_> (his name being Scamandrius), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:22:506\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.506</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Ἄρκτος, ἣν καὶ Ἄμαξαν ἐ</foreign>. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">καλέουσι</foreign> which they <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">call also</tr_> the Wain, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:18:487\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.487</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:138\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.138</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:22:29\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.29</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Τιτῆνας ἐ. καλέεσκεν . . τιταίνοντας ἀτασθαλίῃ μέγα ῥέξαι ἔργον</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">named</tr_> them Titans, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">after</tr_> their endeavouring . . (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ἐπὶ τῷ τιταίνειν</etym>), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0020.tlg001.perseus-grc1:207\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hes.\">Hes.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">207</biblScope> </bibl>; so in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author></bibl>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐ. δὲ ἡ κρήνη ἐπικαλέεται Ἡλίου</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:181\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.181</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Ἀθηναίης ἐ</foreign>. <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">Ἀσσησίης</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:19\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.19</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; also, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">in name only, nominally</tr_>, [<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Μενέσθιον] τέκε Πολυδώρη</foreign> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Σπερχειῷ, αὐτὰρ ἐ. Βώρῳ</foreign> she bare him to Spercheius (really), but <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">nominally</tr_> to Borus, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:16:177\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.177</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὸν τοῦ βουκόλου ἐπίκλησιν παῖδα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:114\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.114</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κατ᾽ ἐ</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0548.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:3:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Apollod.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.3.2</biblScope> </bibl>; opp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὄνομα</foreign>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0081.tlg001:5:21\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.H.\">D.H.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.21</biblScope></bibl>. </sense><sense n=\"2\" id=\"n39754.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\">. after <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author></bibl>, in other cases, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">surname, name</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.3</biblScope></bibl>, etc. </sense><sense n=\"3\" id=\"n39754.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\">. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">imputation</tr_>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">charge</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:68\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.68</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"Perseus:abo:pap,P.Lille:29:27\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ PLille\">PLille</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">29.27</biblScope> </bibl> <date TEIform=\"date\">(iii B.C.)</date>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\